casebody.data:
Michael ROACH, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0636 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The applicant appeals the summary dismissal of his fourth application for postconviction relief challenging his 2004 convictions for murder in the second degree and robbery in the first degree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
